{"tid":549301,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"名古屋景點一問","createTime":"2018-02-03T13:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T15:58:14.000Z","uid":10974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c2e34b019729a0a1edd14395949cbed737e2ee","tid":549301,"uid":10974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:10:03.000Z","msg":"想請教下咁多位巴打<br />\n我2月尾會同屋企人去自駕遊中北陸, 其中PLAN左會停留名古屋兩日<br />\n諗住第一日:<br />\n上就去摘士多啤梨 <br />\n下就去熱田神宮 &amp; 白鳥庭園<br />\n黃昏時間去名花之里<br />\n最後夜晚去蓬莱軒 松坂屋店食 <br />\n或者去綠洲21睇下 因為酒店係附近<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日:<br />\n上就去名古屋城<br />\n下就去栄 / 栄附近地下街 / 名古屋電視塔 行下<br />\n夜晚未諗到去邊好<br />\n<br />\n因為屋企人好似對博物館興趣不大<br />\n所以想請教下大家意見有咩地方 同 餐廳推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b773074f03b5c52111afe5908b350fdca4b4721","tid":549301,"uid":10974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cad5ac39a80e2c488c31fdef58f992211dd384","tid":549301,"uid":10974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"一推再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad5a82d28f2aa0ab316f30b6b0f8cf7ba868a39","tid":549301,"uid":10974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人去過竹島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e7fe25ca3ad1289ccc8dd974b70af2ee84ade0","tid":549301,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"去唐吉訶德掃貨"},{"pid":"148311bb1dc3906bfb587d41f45b191fb1d2e21e","tid":549301,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"去機舖打太鼓，夾公仔"},{"p